om tradition and use a \\u00a31.9million prize pot to remunerate its champions.\", \"from\": 382, \"to\": 491, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"World Athleticshas\", \"from\": 382, \"to\": 400}, {\"ngram\": \"tradition\", \"from\": 421, \"to\": 430}, {\"ngram\": \"a \\u00a31.9million prize pot\", \"from\": 439, \"to\": 462}, {\"ngram\": \"its champions\", \"from\": 477, \"to\": 490}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The sport's governing body also plans to stretch the prize pot for the subsequent summer Olympics in Los Angeles with financial rewards for the silver and bronze medallists.\", \"from\": 493, \"to\": 666, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 594, \"end\": 605, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\", \"score\": 0.9999998821463193, \"rank\": 9.040569204481081e-08, \"text\": \"Los Angeles\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The sport's governing body\", \"from\": 493, \"to\": 519}, {\"ngram\": \"the prize pot\", \"from\": 542, \"to\": 555}, {\"ngram\": \"the subsequent summer Olympics\", \"from\": 560, \"to\": 590}, {\"ngram\": \"financial rewards\", \"from\": 611, \"to\": 628}, {\"ngram\": \"the silver and bronze medallists\", \"from\": 633, \"to\": 665}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Individual champions will net \\u00a340,000 in Paris with relay teams sharing a similar prize pot in their events.\", \"from\": 668, \"to\": 776, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 709, \"end\": 714, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999478257009, \"rank\": 5.217434277228319e-08, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Individual champions\", \"from\": 668, \"to\": 688}, {\"ngram\": \"relay teams\", \"from\": 720, \"to\": 731}, {\"ngram\": \"a similar prize pot\", \"from\": 740, \"to\": 759}, {\"ngram\": \"their events\", \"from\": 763, \"to\": 775}]}, {\"sentence\": \"All gold medallists must pass the necessary anti-doping controls to earn their payday.\", \"from\": 777, \"to\": 863, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"All gold medallists\", \"from\": 777, \"to\": 796}, {\"ngram\": \"the necessary anti-doping controls\", \"from\": 807, \"to\": 841}, {\"ngram\": \"their payday\", \"from\": 850, \"to\": 862}]}, {\"sentence\": \"World Athletics presidentSeb Coesaid: \\\"The introduction of prize money for Olympic gold medallists is a pivotal moment for World Athletics and the sport of athletics as a whole, underscoring our commitment to empowering the athletes and recognising the critical role they play in the success of any Olympic Games.\", \"from\": 865, \"to\": 1178, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 988, \"end\": 1003, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/World_Athletics\", \"score\": 0.9999998674886771, \"rank\": 1.3251123362626364e-07, \"text\": \"World Athletics\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/World_Athletics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/World_Athletics\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"World Athletics presidentSeb Coesaid\", \"from\": 865, \"to\": 901}, {\"ngram\": \"The introduction\", \"from\": 904, \"to\": 920}, {\"ngram\": \"prize money\", \"from\": 924, \"to\": 935}, {\"ngram\": \"Olympic gold medallists\", \"from\": 940, \"to\": 963}, {\"ngram\": \"a pivotal moment\", \"from\": 967, \"to\": 983}, {\"ngram\": \"the sport\", \"from\": 1008, \"to\": 1017}, {\"ngram\": \"athletics\", \"from\": 1021, \"to\": 1030}, {\"ngram\": \"a whole\", \"from\": 1034, \"to\": 1041}, {\"ngram\": \"our commitment\", \"from\": 1056, \"to\": 1070}, {\"ngram\": \"the athletes\", \"from\": 1085, \"to\": 1097}, {\"ngram\": \"the critical role\", \"from\": 1114, \"to\": 1131}, {\"ngram\": \"the success\", \"from\": 1145, \"to\": 1156}, {\"ngram\": \"any Olympic Games\", \"from\": 1160, \"to\": 1177}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"This is the continuation of a journey we started back in 2015, which sees all the money World Athletics receives from theInternational Olympic Committeefor the Olympic Games go directly back into our sport.\", \"from\": 1180, \"to\": 1387, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1269, \"end\": 1284, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/World_Athletics\", \"score\": 0.9999998674886771, \"rank\": 1.3251123362626364e-07, \"text\": \"World Athletics\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/World_Athletics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/World_Athletics\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the continuation\", \"from\": 1189, \"to\": 1205}, {\"ngram\": \"a journey\", \"from\": 1209, \"to\": 1218}, {\"ngram\": \"all the money\", \"from\": 1255, \"to\": 1268}, {\"ngram\": \"theInternational Olympic\", \"from\": 1299, \"to\": 1323}, {\"ngram\": \"Committeefor the Olympic Games\", \"from\": 1324, \"to\": 1354}, {\"ngram\": \"our sport\", \"from\": 1377, \"to\": 1386}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We started with the Olympic dividend payments to our member federations, which saw us distribute an extra US$5m a year on top of existing grants aimed at athletics growth projects, and we are now in a position to also fund gold medal performances for athletes in Paris, with a commitment to reward all three medallists at the LA28 Olympic Games.\", \"from\": 1389, \"to\": 1735, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1653, \"end\": 1658, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999478257009, \"rank\": 5.217434277228319e-08, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the Olympic dividend payments\", \"from\": 1406, \"to\": 1435}, {\"ngram\": \"our member federations\", \"from\": 1439, \"to\": 1461}, {\"ngram\": \"us\", \"from\": 1473, \"to\": 1475}, {\"ngram\": \"an extra US$5m\", \"from\": 1487, \"to\": 1501}, {\"ngram\": \"top\", \"from\": 1512, \"to\": 1515}, {\"ngram\": \"existing grants\", \"from\": 1519, \"to\": 1534}, {\"ngram\": \"athletics growth projects\", \"from\": 1544, \"to\": 1569}, {\"ngram\": \"a position\", \"from\": 1589, \"to\": 1599}, {\"ngram\": \"gold medal performances\", \"from\": 1613, \"to\": 1636}, {\"ngram\": \"athletes\", \"from\": 1641, \"to\": 1649}, {\"ngram\": \"a commitment\", \"from\": 1665, \"to\": 1677}, {\"ngram\": \"all three medallists\", \"from\": 1688, \"to\": 1708}, {\"ngram\": \"the LA28 Olympic Games\", \"from\": 1712, \"to\": 1734}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"While it is impossible to put a marketable value on winning an Olympic medal, or on the commitment and focus it takes to even represent your country at an Olympic Games, I think it is important we start somewhere.\\\"\", \"from\": 1737, \"to\": 1952, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a marketable value\", \"from\": 1768, \"to\": 1786}, {\"ngram\": \"an Olympic medal\", \"from\": 1798, \"to\": 1814}, {\"ngram\": \"the commitment\", \"from\": 1822, \"to\": 1836}, {\"ngram\": \"your country\", \"from\": 1874, \"to\": 1886}, {\"ngram\": \"an Olympic Games\", \"from\": 1890, \"to\": 1906}]}, {\"sentence\": \"MORE ABOUT Have your say... 1 Crime Fight breaks out on Elizabeth line train after youths told to stop vaping by middle-aged passenger Fight breaks out on Elizabeth line after youths told to stop vaping 2 Football Liverpool XI vs Brighton: Starting lineup, confirmed team news, injury latest for Premier League today Liverpool XI vs Brighton: Starting lineup and confirmed team news 3 UK Flights alert: UK issues global travel disruption warning over Donald Trump's Iran war Flights alert: UK issues global travel disruption warning on Iran war 4 Lifestyle Horoscope today: Your daily guide for Saturday, March 21, 2026 Horoscope today: Your daily guide for Saturday, March 21, 